- I think this is gonna work.

12:45.639 --> 12:47.473
There you go, Chair.

12:47.475 --> 12:49.275
Here comes the baby.

12:49.277 --> 12:50.409
Oh.

12:50.411 --> 12:53.545
- Yes, hi, Dr. Goldberg.
- Garfield.

12:53.547 --> 12:54.546
Wait, doctor?

12:54.548 --> 12:55.814
You're a doctor?

12:55.816 --> 12:58.684
- Why aren't you doing this?
- No, no, no.

12:58.686 --> 13:00.819
I'd probably
just muck everything up,

13:00.821 --> 13:03.389
what with my years
of intensive medical training,

13:03.391 --> 13:04.857
my degree in
the medical field--

13:04.859 --> 13:06.092
Why are you being
so passive-aggressive?

13:06.094 --> 13:08.828
I'll tell you what.
You keep delivering the baby,

13:08.830 --> 13:11.330
I'll go downstairs,
grab some Borax

13:11.332 --> 13:13.498
and cleaning utensils,
and I'll scrub the floors!

13:13.500 --> 13:15.901
We're gonna kill them both!

13:15.903 --> 13:17.370
- Please!
- Please what?

13:17.372 --> 13:18.570
- Please help!
- Doc--

13:18.572 --> 13:21.006
- Doctor.
- Doctor, that's right.

13:21.008 --> 13:23.809
I am trained in the medical
profession and here to help.

13:23.811 --> 13:26.245
I'm going to need
the greatest technology

13:26.247 --> 13:28.646
medicine has to offer--
a wet rag and a scalpel.

13:28.648 --> 13:31.787
Let's get this baby born.

13:34.323 --> 13:36.322
Now, Commodore,
I think we need to discuss

13:36.324 --> 13:37.190
these donations to charity.

13:37.192 --> 13:39.158
The only charity
I donate to

13:39.160 --> 13:40.860
is the Men's Health Clinic
of Newport.

13:40.862 --> 13:43.495
And that's specifically
for finding a cure for syphilis.

13:47.269 --> 13:49.503
In the last decade,
your wife has donated

13:49.505 --> 13:52.739
over $50 million
to various charities

13:52.741 --> 13:54.674
in the greater Newport area.

13:54.676 --> 13:56.809
What?
Dodo!

13:56.811 --> 14:00.114
I'll destroy her!

14:00.116 --> 14:01.815
<i>Dodo's ruined me!</i>

14:01.817 --> 14:03.283
If she has been spending
without your consent,

14:03.285 --> 14:06.152
you have every reason
to get rid of her.

14:06.154 --> 14:07.721
Kill her with my bare hands,
you say?

14:07.723 --> 14:10.856
Oh!

14:10.858 --> 14:12.158
<i>Uh, no.</i>

14:12.160 --> 14:13.994
That's a bit messy.

14:13.996 --> 14:16.363
Just send her away.

14:16.365 --> 14:17.129
Right.

14:17.131 --> 14:21.902
Hobson, contact the asylum.

14:21.904 --> 14:24.070
Dodo's going jacket shopping...

14:24.072 --> 14:25.938
straitjacket shopping!

14:27.541 --> 14:30.744
Madam. Madam!
Listen to me.

14:30.746 --> 14:32.578
You are in grave danger.
You must come with me now!

14:32.580 --> 14:37.517
Oh, Peepers, I haven't come
since the Polk administration.

14:37.519 --> 14:39.352
This is no time
for joking, madam,

14:39.354 --> 14:41.888
although I found that remark
very funny.

14:41.890 --> 14:43.490
I jest not, hireling.

14:43.492 --> 14:45.258
I am no longer
an orgasmic woman.

14:45.260 --> 14:48.595
Not even the bumpiest
of carriage rides

14:48.597 --> 14:49.863
can grape my raisin.

14:49.865 --> 14:51.331
Lady Dodo, please!

14:51.333 --> 14:53.866
The Commodore is going to-- oh!

14:53.868 --> 14:54.734
Leave me be, Peepers.

14:54.736 --> 14:57.437
That is an order.

14:57.439 --> 14:59.739
I will meet my fate
as I choose.

15:02.243 --> 15:04.443
As you wish, madam.

